Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.99,0:00:42.96,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚木

Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:48.40,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闇と遊ぶ星たちへ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:53.06,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛を歌い　飽きつくした
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.28,0:00:57.66,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏を灯し　雛菊の
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:03.28,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢に寄り添う爪の痕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.89,0:01:11.31,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唇から唇へと伝い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.61,0:01:15.91,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その温もりはどこへ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.23,0:01:22.41,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辿り付くあてはないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.28,0:01:28.47,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたでなくちゃ　満たせない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.66,0:01:33.10,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私じゃなきゃ　許せなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.33,0:01:37.86,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だから　私はこの足で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:40.22,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立ち上がれて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.42,0:01:42.62,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ぞっとしたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.78,0:01:47.22,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飼い殺しなら　救われる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.43,0:01:51.95,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,でも見事に　鍵は外れて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.14,0:02:02.86,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私はまるで　鳥籠を欲している狂う籠鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:10.66,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘を抱いた花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.83,0:00:48.40,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与黑暗游戏的星斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:53.06,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为爱咏唱　我已经厌倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.28,0:00:57.66,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点亮夏季的雏菊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:03.28,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴随梦境的爪痕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.89,0:01:11.31,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过双唇传递而来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.61,0:01:15.91,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份温存将何去何从
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.23,0:01:22.41,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明没有可以前往的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.28,0:01:28.47,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是你　我得不到满足
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.66,0:01:33.10,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是我　是不会原谅你的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.33,0:01:37.86,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我能用自己的双脚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:40.22,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站立起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.42,0:01:42.62,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却感到心惊胆寒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.78,0:01:47.22,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果养我一生　我还可以得救
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.43,0:01:51.95,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是　锁却顺利打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.14,0:02:02.86,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我宛如为渴求鸟笼而疯狂的笼中之鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.12,0:02:10.72,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀抱谎言的花

Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.70,0:22:54.69,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見てて　ご覧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.94,0:23:00.34,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほら　満ちぬけた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.41,0:23:05.29,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溢れた傍から
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:11.12,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消えて　抜け殻に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.96,0:23:21.11,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流されて　辿り付く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.65,0:23:27.00,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現　蕩ける
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.67,0:23:33.11,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天この魂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.44,0:23:43.62,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢　紡いだ夢を　どうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.89,0:23:52.67,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その小指に絡めなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.95,0:23:56.99,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛んだ刺は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.96,0:24:03.14,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一つ抜ける
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.85,0:24:08.13,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取る　抜ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.70,0:22:54.69,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请注意看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.94,0:23:00.34,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊　充满了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.41,0:23:05.29,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从溢出的一侧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:11.12,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐渐消失　变成了空壳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.96,0:23:21.11,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随波逐流　到达彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.65,0:23:27.00,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉醉于现实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.67,0:23:33.11,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天上的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.44,0:23:43.62,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦　编织的梦境　请看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.89,0:23:52.67,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请缠绕我的小指不放开
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.95,0:23:56.99,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼痛的刺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.96,0:24:03.14,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一根被拔掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.85,0:24:08.13,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取出　拔掉

Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.05,0:00:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山河三岔路 别离之路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.18,0:00:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要保护的是自己 是他人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.41,0:00:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是常世的黑暗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.58,0:00:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是非对错无法补偿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.43,0:00:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有终结的深仇大恨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.47,0:00:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭转时空 打开大门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.30,0:00:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难报之怨 我为您报
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.90,0:00:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你哦

Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.58,0:02:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.74,0:02:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么让我看到这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.77,0:02:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校的事情也是因为你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.23,0:02:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了很过分的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜做这些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.71,0:02:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就那么想让我成为地狱少女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.71,0:02:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是说点什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说啊 阎魔爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的魔法失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会成为什么地狱少女的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.94,0:03:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再出现在我眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.31,0:03:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你搞的鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.72,0:03:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚木 欢迎回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸已经回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.22,0:03:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样 别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.48,0:03:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚木 去了哪里买东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,及川商店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 有土豆 有红萝卜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有肉 还有长葱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:03:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买了这么多啊 真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.85,0:04:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么要给你奖赏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.79,0:04:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚木 这是给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.36,0:04:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.34,0:04:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小熊 小熊 是小熊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸给你的礼物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.79,0:04:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能小看小钢珠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.72,0:04:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点早 这是生日礼物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻子好可爱啊 小熊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚木 还没对爸爸说谢谢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.06,0:04:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈也有附赠的哦 看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈的也是小熊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说什么附赠的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.17,0:04:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可本来就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是谁教你的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.10,0:04:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.17,0:05:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一站是南台下 南台下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要下车的乘客请按铃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.09,0:05:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹车 失灵了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快请外科部长来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20点19分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的 亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸 爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.41,0:06:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 别慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.58,0:06:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我儿子死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家请冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.64,0:06:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司机呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.31,0:06:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙也死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:06:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要死的话也别这么快死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:06:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没承担责任就死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.70,0:07:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在都是这种状况了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.43,0:07:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么请你们到走廊说给我听好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.67,0:07:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忍受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.91,0:07:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少给我看看他的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.78,0:07:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于最近发生的事故
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请允许我做出报告
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.44,0:07:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据内部调查的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事故车辆的设备没有找到任何异常
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:07:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说不是因为设备不良吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是乘客的证言中有人指出「刹车失灵了」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有发现任何设备不完善的状况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.99,0:08:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因而得出了结论 事故是由人为因素造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是辻乃桥运输公司方面没有任何责任吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们公司将负起责任 对受害者家属做出赔偿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.80,0:08:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样是说 是死亡的司机的过失吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说责任在司机身上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.01,0:08:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.79,0:08:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 接下来就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 会长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:08:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:08:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了吗
